      "description": "<span style=\"color:red\"><strong>Please Note:</strong></span> <em>Due to printing inconsistencies, versions of this card can have either foiling over the entire face of the card or foiling on only the borders of the card, along with foiling color variations for each. You may receive any variation unless specifically noted as a <a href=\"https://help.tcgplayer.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000111067-How-Do-Listings-With-Photos-Work-\">Listing with Photo</a>.</em><br><br>\r\nReveal cards from the top of your library until you reveal a nonland card. Put the revealed cards on the bottom of your library in a random order. When you reveal a nonland card this way, Calibrated Blast deals damage equal to that card's mana value to any target.\r\n<br>Flashback 3RR",
